<h3 id="default">Manage default zone</h3>	
<p>Default zone is the main zone which is applied to shipping and taxation if no defined zones are available / applicable.</p>	


<h3 id="create">Create delivery zone</h3>	
<p>To add a new delivery zone:</p>	
<ul>
	<li>Click add new zone</li>
	<li>Enter zone's name</li>
	<li>Group countries by adding them to the left "country" box</li>
